00:20:19,080 --> 00:20:19,920
Baik.

232
00:20:23,680 --> 00:20:26,240
Bagaimana? Kita bercinta?

233
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:32,040
Baik. Waktunya tidak tepat?

234
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:38,320
Jadi, saatnya berpesta?

235
00:20:42,040 --> 00:20:43,120
Saatnya berpesta.

236
00:20:53,960 --> 00:20:55,440
Hei, ayolah.

